# Normalize line endings for Git on Windows
* text=auto eol=lf
# PowerShell scripts need CRLF on Windows execution, but keep source as LF?
# Best practice for cross-platform PowerShell core: LF
# Best practice for Windows PowerShell 5.1: Let Git handle text conversion.
# We will enforce LF for storage to avoid clutter, PS Core handles LF fine.

# Denote linguist
*.ps1 linguist-language=PowerShell